===所获奖励===
1978年沃兹涅先斯基被授予[[苏联国家奖金|苏联国家奖金]]。<ref name="Russian poet Andrei Voznesensky dies aged 77"/> 他是十个学院的名誉成员，包括俄罗斯文学院，美国艺术和文学学院，巴黎龚古尔文学院。
2008年12月23日，俄罗斯总统[[德米特里·阿纳托利耶维奇·梅德韦杰夫|梅德韦杰夫]]在克里姆林宫授予沃兹涅先斯基二级[[祖国功勋勋章|祖国功勋勋章]]。<ref name="Venturesome poet Andrei Voznesensky dies at 77">{{cite web|author=Heintz,im|url=http://www.boston.com/ae/celebrity/articles/2010/06/01/venturesome_poet_andrei_voznesensky_dies_at_77/|title=Venturesome poet Andrei Voznesensky dies at 77|date=2010-06-01|accessdate=2010-06-01|publisher=''[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]''|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055203/http://www.boston.com/ae/celebrity/articles/2010/06/01/venturesome_poet_andrei_voznesensky_dies_at_77/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

